Used to iterate over a slice.

# Types

## SliceIterator {#zero_SliceIterator}

```C
typedef struct SliceIterator(T)
```

SliceIterator(T) holds the slice, and the current position into it.

# Normal functions

## next_SliceIterator_\$T {#one_next_SliceIterator_QordninetwoEQDT}

```C
Option(ref(T)) next_SliceIterator_$T(SliceIterator(T) *self)
```

Get a reference to the next element in the slice that this
iterator is iterating over, or None if the end was reached.
